('ONET-GEOTHERMAL_TECHNICIANS', 'source_onet_geothermal_technicians', 'Geothermal Technicians', 'Geothermal Technicians is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Perform technical activities at power plants or individual installations necessary for the generation of power from geothermal energy sources. Monitor and control operating activities at geothermal power generation facilities and perform maintenance and repairs as necessary. Install, test, and maintain residential and commercial geothermal heat pumps.', ARRAY['Corrosion Technician','Design Technician','Distribution Field Technician','Field Distribution Technician','Geothermal Field Technician','Geothermal HVAC Technician (Geothermal Heating, Ventilating, and Air Conditioning Technician)','Geothermal Installer','Geothermal Service Technician','Geothermal System Installer','Geothermal Technician','Ground Source Heat Pump Technician (GSHP Technician)','I and C Technician (Instrument and Controls Technician)','I and E Technician (Instrumentation and Electrical Technician)','I C and E Technician (Instrumentation, Control, and Electrical Technician)','Operations and Maintenance Technician (O and M Technician)','Operations Technician','Operator Technician','Plant Electrical Technician','Plant Mechanic','Plant Technician','Pump Technician','Switchgear Operator']::text[], ARRAY['Geothermal Technicians','Corrosion Technician','Design Technician','Distribution Field Technician','Field Distribution Technician','Geothermal Field Technician','Geothermal HVAC Technician (Geothermal Heating, Ventilating, and Air Conditioning Technician)','Geothermal Installer','Geothermal Service Technician','Geothermal System Installer','Geothermal Technician','Ground Source Heat Pump Technician (GSHP Technician)','I and C Technician (Instrument and Controls Technician)','I and E Technician (Instrumentation and Electrical Technician)','I C and E Technician (In